model.graphTransformer
Class EdgeVariableAssignment

java.lang.Object
  model.graphTransformer.VariableAssignment
      model.graphTransformer.EdgeVariableAssignment

public class EdgeVariableAssignment
extends VariableAssignment

EdgeVariableAssignment Represents a pairing of a variable edge and a constant edge. This class is used differently from NodeVariableAssignment. Dealg means at first edge var assignments will be made as node variable assignments. After realg, the node var assignments that are actually for edges will be translated into objects of this class.
